Package model.fsa.ver1 Description

model.fsa.ver1 - The package containing an implementation of the interfaces in package model.fsa, namely a model of a finite state automaton.

This package contains an implementation of a data structure representing an abstract model of finite state machine. In this case it is a model an automaton in the workspace.
